simply-journal-admin (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Install into a dedicated virtual environment under
    /opt/simply-journal-admin/venv instead of the system Python interpreter;
    drop the --break-system-packages workflow.
  * Ship the wheel under /opt/simply-journal-admin/wheel and add a
    /usr/bin/simply-journal-admin wrapper that invokes the venv entry point.
  * Keep the package CLI-only; do not register a systemd service during
    installation.
  * Drop the python3-pip dependency; add python3-venv.

